-14T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">中共不滅香港不會好</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全球10月1日圍你老母中國大使館</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaL53Ur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaL53Ur.png&h=d3b46782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>贈慶要點:</strong><br />\n1. 呼籲外國停止在中國投資<br />\n2. 呼籲外國停止從中國購買<br />\n3. 呼籲外國政府凍結中國官員海外資產<br />\n4. 鼓勵全球民眾, 10月1日到附近中國大使館&quot;贈慶&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>贈慶四步曲:</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">1) 在自己的社交媒體上分享影片文宣：</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n影片Youtube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=15pbHsNjazE&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D15pbHsNjazE%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=da82b370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=15pbHsNjazE&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n影片高清檔歡迎不問自取:<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1TZgmVUKc1PEg6EBcwd1yYFE3PtKhQwrg/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1TZgmVUKc1PEg6EBcwd1yYFE3PtKhQwrg%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=8c58a2f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1TZgmVUKc1PEg6EBcwd1yYFE3PtKhQwrg/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n文宣：<br />\n10月1日到附近中國大使館&quot;贈慶&quot;:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hTZiEnu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhTZiEnu.jpg&h=d65e6bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n停止在中國投資:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWHTti4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWHTti4.jpg&h=5b8807b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n停止從中國購買:<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vuMwZqP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvuMwZqP.jpg&h=85d54003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凍結中國官員海外資產:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VsjVGEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVsjVGEi.jpg&h=f8e056b6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2) 簽聯署, 我們會把簽名送到各國政要和全球500強的非中國公司:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/g7-stop-invest-in-china-stop-buying-from-china-freeze-chinese-officials-overseas-assets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fg7-stop-invest-in-china-stop-buying-from-china-freeze-chinese-officials-overseas-assets&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=08b9f4b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/g7-stop-invest-in-china-stop-buying-from-china-freeze-chinese-officials-overseas-assets</a><br />\n3）在facebook上轉 &quot; No Chinazi&quot; profile特效框:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/profilepicframes/?selected_overlay_id=646419452428398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fprofilepicframes%2F%3Fselected_overlay_id%3D646419452428398&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=3e68b728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/profilepicframes/?selected_overlay_id=646419452428398</a><br />\n4) 約朋友在10月1日到附近的中國大使館贈慶<br />\nFollow us on Facebook: No Chinazi, 追擊赤色十月 The Hunt For Red October<br />\nwebsite: <a href=\"http://www.nochinazi.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nochinazi.org&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=e3ee6087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.nochinazi.org</a><br />\nTwitter: BoycottChina"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:42:02.000Z","msg":"（重要）大家千祈唔好做以下的事<br />\n1.不要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捐款支持連登登報慶祝國慶</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/g20celebratemotherbirthday/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fg20celebratemotherbirthday%2F&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=aac3d7e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/g20celebratemotherbirthday/</a><br />\n，不要有錢出錢，不要有力出力（share,推）<br />\n2.不要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">塗污紙幣，在上面寫口號</span></span></strong>，這是違法的，而且浪費紙張和墨水，不環保，尤其不要塗污港幣和人民幣，這是有辱國體的<br />\n3.不要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去藍絲商戶集體排隊齋坐借廁所無幫襯</span></span></strong>，這會影響他們生計的<br />\n4.不要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以貼紙來張貼連儂牆</span></span></strong>，因為貼紙既放防水又難撕，這會另藍絲搣到發脾氣兼指甲都披埋，很可憐的<br />\n麻煩大家幫手推<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1572232/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1572232/page/1</a>"}]}